{"tid":1159710,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個俾人插隊嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-05-18T02:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T01:29:03.000Z","uid":179902,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac3a782041fd6e2916cdb4b5a35433f8a54535d","tid":1159710,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"之前試過喺超級市場排隊俾錢嘅時候，下個就到我，有個香港大媽突然插入我前面，然後話自己買少少野俾佢排先，嗰次第一次俾人插隊，唔識反應就俾佢打左尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後唸番就好慶，點解要犧牲我同後面排隊嘅人嘅時間，去遷就你條仆街大媽？你啲時間係錢，我嗰啲時間就唔係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過呢次之後，我發誓我再俾人無禮打尖，我一定開聲屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c879638b19b666b255b7f4fa1bac0319dcf48b4","tid":1159710,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"現場屌佢一句： 我都趕時間，你唔得閒排隊咪唔好買"},{"pid":"f80eb42f2efd55e1eb2ab13342c66372ffd49577","tid":1159710,"uid":165244,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"去海洋公園玩<br />\n9個鬼妹慢慢由好後tun到我前面<br />\n我同個朋友傾緊計所以到我意識到佢地搏懵嗰陣已經有5個鬼妹行左去前面<br />\n我朋友話唔好咁多事啦 唔打都打左<br />\n但係真係忍唔到 同前面一個鬼妹講excuse me ladies are you supposed to be here<br />\n佢話yeah<br />\n我就話you guys are jumping the queue and you should be ashamed of yourself<br />\n佢地唔理我 係咁叫我後面嗰4個鬼妹上埋去<br />\n後面嗰幾個唔敢打我尖 係咁叫前面嗰d返返去後面 因為老豆老母吩咐左要一齊坐<br />\n一路前後前後互叫之後 最後佢地無得一齊坐<br />\n前面嗰班早我兩隻船 後面嗰幾個仲要同我坐 <br />\n的確有d尷尬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007929cef79bec350033152ce27f126f1e33406e","tid":1159710,"uid":838,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"挑隊過關嗰時有個大嬸喺左面條隊插過嚟<br />\n我捉住佢膊頭拉開佢，然後入閘<br />\n個大嬸嚇親，然後道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4b366701a5e7a8af70ff74b1b5b19442d7d873","tid":1159710,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007929cef79bec350033152ce27f126f1e33406e","tid":1159710,"uid":838,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"挑隊過關嗰時有個大嬸喺左面條隊插過嚟<br />\n我捉住佢膊頭拉開佢，然後入閘<br />\n個大嬸嚇親，然後道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"正確做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班大嬸真係人善人欺"},{"pid":"6ff4a8fb3b7b33f70062550e4c626882c8118852","tid":1159710,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:47:35.000Z","msg":"打尖呀戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n睇左俾人插既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4dcbd64ae75db6d1ae553714e3a4a7c62f6e3c","tid":1159710,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80eb42f2efd55e1eb2ab13342c66372ffd49577","tid":1159710,"uid":165244,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"去海洋公園玩<br />\n9個鬼妹慢慢由好後tun到我前面<br />\n我同個朋友傾緊計所以到我意識到佢地搏懵嗰陣已經有5個鬼妹行左去前面<br />\n我朋友話唔好咁多事啦 唔打都打左<br />\n但係真係忍唔到 同前面一個鬼妹講excuse me ladies are you supposed to be here<br />\n佢話yeah<br />\n我就話you guys are jumping the queue and you should be ashamed of yourself<br />\n佢地唔理我 係咁叫我後面嗰4個鬼妹上埋去<br />\n後面嗰幾個唔敢打我尖 係咁叫前面嗰d返返去後面 因為老豆老母吩咐左要一齊坐<br />\n一路前後前後互叫之後 最後佢地無得一齊坐<br />\n前面嗰班早我兩隻船 後面嗰幾個仲要同我坐 <br />\n的確有d尷尬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"想幫巴打含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2ecb59053d138bbc84a76c33b1c6a515c111c9","tid":1159710,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6ff4a8fb3b7b33f70062550e4c626882c8118852","tid":1159710,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:47:35.000Z","msg":"打尖呀戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n睇左俾人插既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"眼殘就睇眼科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74b20adc48139e2466bcbc158252810199da5c2","tid":1159710,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"廢老成日打尖，就算得幾丁友排都要打尖"},{"pid":"d3602ea1141d770d0dd0db884af9c6d47f53d5be","tid":1159710,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c74b20adc48139e2466bcbc158252810199da5c2","tid":1159710,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"廢老成日打尖，就算得幾丁友排都要打尖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"呢個真，自私到仆街"},{"pid":"b8b6a0d550c57322945b5e75a61e5cba46351466","tid":1159710,"uid":145019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"有次同fd搭巴士<br />\n本身我同佢都已經排係隊尾<br />\n點知有個呀叔都要插埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個fd已經即刻出聲:唔撚係呀,咁都要打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到上車果下,咁啱比我個fd見到個呀叔係2蚊搭車<br />\n之後我個fd好大聲爆左句:哦,原來2蚊既,係咁上下架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係隔離笑撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00884f43e6a34f4f5d6edad8b730fa7a37cbd1a1","tid":1159710,"uid":153963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"外國機場 入境做安檢 比3 4個大陸𡃁仔打尖 我叫佢去隊尾排 佢唔肯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住我屋企人同幾個香港人一齊屌佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b9f793f152e2b49c055ccbb154852bc6558320","tid":1159710,"uid":252660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"每次俾人打尖 我都會大大聲出聲屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多經驗 通常啲仆街都係面懵懵死返去後面排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485db19373e751c0e20821f741b6b832fc62084f","tid":1159710,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"係支那買火車飛，比個阿叔陰陰濕濕插隊<br />\n<br />\n臨到櫃位時超前敲窗講呢條友打尖，後面有人幫口，所以職員趕佢再排隊，打尖阿叔白白排左廿分鐘"},{"pid":"787ff73995ca22e7c5d117fbca2463fbe50c0181","tid":1159710,"uid":50641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:59:00.000Z","msg":"有次同媽子係百佳買野<br />\n有個大陸佬無啦啦打媽咪尖 話買支豆漿 好快<br />\n我一手抽個大陸佬出黎佢跌落地<br />\n之後我就屌鳩佢：<br />\n屌你老味 我話鳩之你買乜撚野 <br />\n呢到係香港 講規矩既 買野就排隊啦<br />\n之後個大陸鳩就發脾氣話：唔撚買啦<br />\n跟住就走撚左"},{"pid":"44c8ef4f521df76f5d4a7a4fb65e52fc95423f0c","tid":1159710,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"遇到幾個紋身大漢打尖，我即刻讓俾佢地兼粒聲唔出。"},{"pid":"8028a9f69fd4a4060835c85197fb0c79acb723b0","tid":1159710,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"有2個<br />\n1 係惠康買嘢拎好曬d嘢，咁排排下見到雪糕櫃拎番2個先 咁就比人打左尖，係師奶來都仲要打我尖<br />\n<br />\n2 唔知算唔算打尖 但個感受幾似<br />\n搭地鐵果陣隔離味有啲玻璃挨嘅，咁我無位坐味挨囉，點知無啦啦有個廢老呀伯(拎拐杖)企起我前面想貼住我咁，唔知係味見我女仔就好恰啲，咁我味去第2度企囉"},{"pid":"b2e551e9a29b4b85fb905d294e1d09fb431137b8","tid":1159710,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:29:03.000Z","msg":"去支那公幹，過關d 支那狗一班十幾條友喺側邊有位就攝<br />\n期間不斷有人打尖，排咗好耐條隊都冇郁過<br />\n後尾我索性就咁拉開個欄直接行去counter前面排第二，打咗成百幾條友尖<br />\n奇在班友係零反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}